      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Melt 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[40g] </span><strong>butter</strong> in a pot with a matching lid over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [40g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and stir with a wooden spoon for 1-2 min or until a sandy paste forms</p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min, stirring frequently, until the roux has browned – this is your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>roux</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
