    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> sliced onion</strong> to the pot with brown roux</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for 3-4 min, stirring occasionally, or until starting to soften</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p>",
