    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> sweet potato[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(skin on) into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>Henderson’s Relish</strong>,<strong> tomato paste </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[850ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>Creole-style stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1681314232190-x200.jpg",
