            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate pot with a matching lid over a medium heat and add a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add the<strong> remaining chopped garlic </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
