    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Creole-style haddock & sweet potato stew</strong> in bowls with the <strong>garlic rice</strong> in the centre</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Season generously with<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
